{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>周殷廷 (YT) 今日突然驚爆震撼彈！他在社交平台貼出與陳凱詠 （Jace）極親密的攬攬照，並加上一個心心符號，疑似宣布拍拖，雖然張相睇落舊舊地，但一樣引來不少人留言送上祝福！JACE自從在周殷廷演唱會被對方英雄救美後，二人忽然被Fans「炒CP」，對於有冇發展空間，當時曾與天蠍座拍拖的JACE坦言怕怕。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20250611/1009521254790860800682359.jpeg/DiydX3oj89SbNR2b6VwVNkbY5uj2QnQoz7YPSc-2D0k\" alt=\"陳凱詠（資料圖片)\"><figcaption>陳凱詠（資料圖片)</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20251217/1077997653662896128316580.jpeg/v9XrNZd8oLUljT8i22VT30kMUmttwcpYs1rJj7NayY8\" alt=\"陳凱詠（IG@jacechw）\"><figcaption>陳凱詠（IG@jacechw）</figcaption></figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260421/1123280603119095808248397.jpeg/L14GOh_lF9T2jNYGgfXkDvI0ki6xPwCGBAs9jQQLPY0\"><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260421/1123281386006908928870923.png/BytnwVhd28zuoHwpS7gDG1sZHl4gFPIzfm01iX5tNYk\" alt=\"周殷廷與Jace親密照曝光疑拍拖。（IG@whoisyanting)\"><figcaption>周殷廷與Jace親密照曝光疑拍拖。（IG@whoisyanting)</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-21T09:20:11.495778+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":214,"images":4,"source":"HK01 娛樂","fallback":"none"}}